text: This Is What It Feels Like is the second EP by American singer and songwriter Gracie Abrams. It was released on November 12, 2021, through Interscope Records. It is mainly pop with a mix of bedroom pop and indie pop. Abrams co- wrote all the tracks, and as a producer on "Feels Like". ==References== Category:Gracie Abrams albums
title: This Is What It Feels Like (EP)
